import { Component } from '@angular/core'; import { User } from '../user'; import { LocalStorageService } from '../local-storage.service'; @Component({ selector: 'app-form-page', templateUrl: './form-page.component.html', styleUrls: ['./form-page.component.css'] }) export class FormPageComponent { isSuccess = false; customer: User = { name: '', email: '', phone: '' }; constructor(private localStorageService: LocalStorageService) { } saveCustomer(formData: any) : void { const jsonData = JSON.stringify(this.customer); this.localStorageService.put(formData, jsonData); } submitForm(customerForm: any) { if (customerForm.valid) { console.log('Form Submitted', customerForm.value); } this.isSuccess = true; this.saveCustomer(customerForm); } clearFormData(form: any) { this.localStorageService.clear(form); } }

Customer Form

Phone number is required
